WEBVTT

00:12:59.081 --> 00:13:02.859
And in fact, quite the contrary
to complacency,

00:13:02.883 --> 00:13:06.156
if it were true that 55 years
after the civil rights movement

00:13:06.180 --> 00:13:08.328
there had been no progress
in racial equality,

00:13:08.352 --> 00:13:11.915
the natural conclusion would be,
well, you know, why bother with activism,

00:13:11.939 --> 00:13:13.480
it hasn't accomplished anything.

00:13:13.504 --> 00:13:15.134
And similarly for women's rights.

00:13:15.158 --> 00:13:19.847
The fact that the activism of the past
and other changes have made progress,

00:13:19.871 --> 00:13:22.910
if anything, I think,
emboldens us to seek more.

00:13:22.934 --> 00:13:24.950
CA: I mean, there's this wonderful phrase,

00:13:24.974 --> 00:13:26.744
"Be on the right side of history,"

00:13:26.768 --> 00:13:30.276
which progressives use,
actually, really powerfully,